Task Lock API
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version: 1.0.1
Author: Rowan Lewis <me@rowanlewis.com>
Build Date: 9 February 2009
Requirements: Symphony 2.0.6


Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Upload the "tasklockapi" folder in this archive to your Symphony
   'extensions' folder.

2. Enable it by selecting "Task Lock API", and choosing Enable from the
   with-selected menu, then click Apply.

3. Install and enable the "ASDC" extension:
   http://symphony-cms.com/download/extensions/view/20038/

Example
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

<?php
	
	require_once EXTENSIONS . '/asdc/lib/class.asdc.php';
	require_once EXTENSIONS . '/tasklockapi/extension.driver.php';
	
	$lock = new TaskLock('example');
	
	if ($lock->isActive()) {
		echo 'Locked.';
	}
	
	else {
		$lock->create();
		
		// Do complex processing here:
		
		$lock->remove();
		
		echo 'Done.';
	}
	
?>